      <title>2023 年日本经济将迎来 2500 万游客</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/japan-s-economy-gets-boost-from-25-million-visitors-in-2023</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本在 2023 年迎来了 2500 万名游客，这是自 2019 年以来的最高数字，因为日元疲软有助于吸引大流行后的游客，提振该国脆弱的经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/japan-s-economy-gets-boost-from-25-million-visitors-in-2023</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 07:55:47 GMT</pubDate>
